Name: Average time from SW-Checklist Completed to SW-Awaiting AE Assignment

Name: Total time between SW-Checklist Completed and SW-Awaiting AE Assignment across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Minimum time it takes for SW-Awaiting AE Assignment to occur after SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Average duration of the SW-Awaiting AE Assignment activity itself (i.e., time until the next activity starts)

Name: Average time from SW-Awaiting AE Assignment to SW-Initial Reviewer Selection in variants leading to SW-EIC Reject
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Minimum time between SW-Awaiting AE Assignment and SW-EIC Accept across all successful acceptance paths
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Total time from SW-Awaiting AE Assignment to SW-Awaiting EIC Decision in variants involving multiple reviewer assignment attempts
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Time it takes SW-Awaiting AE Assignment to be followed by SW-Initial Reviewer Selection compared to the time it takes to be followed by Unassign Editor

Name: Average waiting time to SW-Awaiting AE Assignment after Plagiarism Originality Report Completed in standard vs. delayed checklist completion variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Total time from SW-Awaiting AE Assignment to the first occurrence of SW-AE Assign Reviewers in complex reviewer selection variants

Name: Minimum time from SW-Awaiting AE Assignment to SW-EIC Major Revision in revision-intensive process paths

Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Elapsed time between SW-Awaiting AE Assignment and the final decision activity (e.g., SW-EIC Accept, SW-EIC Reject, SW-EIC Major Revision) grouped by variant type
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-EIC Accept'
